axis0.text:
CASE WHEN <%=EDI_Activity%> = 'Send Purchase Order' 
AND PU_COUNT_DISTINCT(EKKO, NAST.NACHA, NAST.KSCHL IN (<%=Send_PO%>))=1
THEN 'One Message Type'
WHEN <%=EDI_Activity%> = 'Send Purchase Order' 
AND PU_COUNT_DISTINCT(EKKO, NAST.NACHA, NAST.KSCHL IN (<%=Send_PO%>))=2
THEN 'Two Message Types'
WHEN <%=EDI_Activity%> = 'Send Purchase Order' 
AND PU_COUNT_DISTINCT(EKKO, NAST.NACHA, NAST.KSCHL IN (<%=Send_PO%>))=3
THEN 'Three Message Types'

WHEN <%=EDI_Activity%> = 'Send Purchase Order Update' 
AND PU_COUNT_DISTINCT(EKKO, NAST.NACHA, NAST.KSCHL IN (<%=Send_PO_Update%>) AND NAST.AENDE = 'X')=1
THEN 'One Message Type'
WHEN <%=EDI_Activity%> = 'Send Purchase Order Update' 
AND PU_COUNT_DISTINCT(EKKO, NAST.NACHA, NAST.KSCHL IN (<%=Send_PO_Update%>) AND NAST.AENDE = 'X')=2
THEN 'Two Message Types'
WHEN <%=EDI_Activity%> = 'Send Purchase Order Update' 
AND PU_COUNT_DISTINCT(EKKO, NAST.NACHA, NAST.KSCHL IN (<%=Send_PO_Update%>) AND NAST.AENDE = 'X')=3
THEN 'Three Message Types'

WHEN <%=EDI_Activity%> = 'Dun Order Confirmation' 
AND PU_COUNT_DISTINCT(EKKO, NAST.NACHA, NAST.KSCHL IN (<%=Dun_Order_Confirmation%>))=1
THEN 'One Message Type'
WHEN <%=EDI_Activity%> = 'Dun Order Confirmation' 
AND PU_COUNT_DISTINCT(EKKO, NAST.NACHA, NAST.KSCHL IN (<%=Dun_Order_Confirmation%>))=2
THEN 'Two Message Types'
WHEN <%=EDI_Activity%> = 'Dun Order Confirmation' 
AND PU_COUNT_DISTINCT(EKKO, NAST.NACHA, NAST.KSCHL IN (<%=Dun_Order_Confirmation%>))=3
THEN 'Three Message Types'


WHEN <%=EDI_Activity%> = 'Send Overdue Notice' 
AND PU_COUNT_DISTINCT(EKKO, NAST.NACHA, NAST.KSCHL IN (<%=Send_Overdue_Notice%>))=1
THEN 'One Message Type'
WHEN <%=EDI_Activity%> = 'Send Overdue Notice' 
AND PU_COUNT_DISTINCT(EKKO, NAST.NACHA, NAST.KSCHL IN (<%=Send_Overdue_Notice%>))=2
THEN 'Two Message Types'
WHEN <%=EDI_Activity%> = 'Send Overdue Notice' 
AND PU_COUNT_DISTINCT(EKKO, NAST.NACHA, NAST.KSCHL IN (<%=Send_Overdue_Notice%>))=3
THEN 'Three Message Types'


ELSE 'N.A.'
END
